                    <li>Excellent connection to the rest of Europe; only 15-minute train travel to central Frankfurt, allowing professionals to attend meetings at short notice.</li>
                    <li>The top-notch dining and frivolous shopping facilities available at the airport also contribute to the most convenient and comforting layover experience, which is why it is among the best airports for busy executives.</li>
                </ul>
